The paper focuses on the visual question answering task, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new method for modeling the relationship and dependency between objects, which involves graph theory and deep learning. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
